                    <span>There is useful information in this book but it<BR>could have been said in about 1/10 of the space.<BR>Concept are repeated ad nauseum. And author uses<BR>ancient GUI styles for examples instead of current<BR>ones. Extremely painful to read.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Thick but absolutely vacuous, platitudinous book</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>1</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
